<h3>How we use information we collect</h3>
<p>We use the information we collect from all of our services to provide, maintain, protect and improve them, to develop new ones, and to protect Creabator and our users. We also use this information to offer you tailored content &ndash; like giving you more relevant search results.</p>
<p>We may use the name you provide for your Creabator Profile across all of the services we offer that require a Creabator Account. In addition, we may replace past names associated with your Creabator Account so that you are represented consistently across all our services. If other users already have your email, or other information that identifies you, we may show them your publicly visible Creabator Profile information, such as your name and photo.</p>
<p>When you contact Creabator, we may keep a record of your communication to help solve any issues you might be facing. We may use your email address to inform you about our services, such as letting you know about upcoming changes or improvements.</p>
